{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my greatest fears were to live through and not to be caught by the Germans and be-- you know, being killed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that was-- that was really the main thing, to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was telling myself all along at that time, well, when I survive, I'm going to buy myself a cow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm going to take it to the pasture so I can milk it, and I can have as much milk and as much sour cream as I really want.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was not the end yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because finally, after we moved out from this place-- which I don't know where it was-- we went somehow to this place, Mochulyanka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was our final-- the last-- the last place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found there, again-- again, my mother-- I-- I know what happened, I think, now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While we were in this-- in the forest, my mother met this man named Goldman who was my father's good friend, and who was really after my mother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he lived with us in-- in Ludvipol, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told my mother that he and some other people are hidden, or staying with this Polish family, Korkus.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if my mother wants to, he will make arrangements so we can stay with them, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was really wonderful, because they were very nice people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, again, we slept on those-- all over the place, and as I said, and if you got that spot on the oven, it was great.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a very nice family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We became really very friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm sure that my mother paid something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I learned how to knit, and I was making socks for them, wool socks.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
